<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吉米是一个贫民。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没有钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没有吃的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他几乎什么也没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吉米花了很多时间寻找工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，他遇到了一位农夫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以为你工作吗？”吉米问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以，但是你必须努力工作。”农夫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我保证，先生。”吉米回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吉米遵守了他的诺言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天吉米都在农场里努力工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫和他的家人都很喜欢吉米。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的女儿经常拿喝的东西给他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吉米喜欢读书和学习。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向自己保证，总有一天，他会摆脱贫困。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会生活得更好。”他发誓说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一天，我会成为很重要的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一有空闲，吉米就读书和学习。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在读什么，吉米？”有一天，农夫的女儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是关于拿破仑的一本书。”吉米回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天，农夫的女儿都会过来跟吉米聊天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们聊书、自然、旅行和他们的梦想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们开始互生爱慕之情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫不知道正在发生的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他看到他们在一起的时候，一切都改变了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了！”农夫大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求您了，先生，我......”吉米试着解释，但是农夫不想听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的女儿不会嫁给一个贫民的！”农夫喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫让吉米离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出去！你竟然敢做出这样的事！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里不再欢迎你了！”他喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可怜的吉米再也说不出一句话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转过身去，头也不回地离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三十五年后的一天，农夫正在清理马鞍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他发现了一个旧袋子，还有几本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些书是吉米的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫打开其中一本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>书里面写着名字：詹姆斯·艾伯拉姆·加菲尔德。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>詹姆斯·艾伯拉姆·加菲尔德是总统的名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吉米是詹姆斯的昵称。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫不敢相信这一切！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吉米竟然就是詹姆斯·艾伯拉姆·加菲尔德总统！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那一天，农夫得到了深刻的教训：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要凭封面来判断一本书的好坏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像不能凭一个人的外表来判断这个人一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吉米信守了对自己的诺言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>离开农场后，他努力地学习和工作，成为了很重要的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从一个贫民变成了美国第二十任总统。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>